HEADWORD: Edifice
<hw>Ed"i*fice</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>aedificium</ets>, fr. <ets>aedificare</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧difice</ets>. See <er>Edify</er>.]</ety> <def>A building; a
